jetAudio HD Music Player Plus 9.4.0 (Patched) - 2018

jetAudio plays almost all digital music files (.wav, .mp3, .ogg, .flac, .m4a, .mpc, .tta, .wv, .ape, .mod, .spx, .opus, .wma *, .mid ** and etc.). In addition, jetAudio provides high-quality sound and offers a wide selection of sound effects, such as stereo widening (X-Wide), reverb (Reverb) and bass boost (X-Bass).

And, in addition to everything else, jetAudio offers 32 blanks for the equalizer, thanks to which you can achieve sound for every taste. And for those who want to achieve special sound, there is a 10- or 20-band graphic equalizer, as well as additional playback settings, including a speed control, smooth transition between tracks (crossfade), AGC system and much more.

Unlike the Basic version, there are no ads in Plus version and additional features are available.
